description:
Guy #1

Straight. 19 years old.

Very business-like. Says he wants to become a millionaire and make "boat loads of money." His plan? Porn!

Guy #2

Straight. 22 years old.

Hot college jock from New York.

Guy #3

Bisexual? 23 years old.

"I'm more straight than anything," he said, "but I can kind of cross over if I need to."

He's never had the "need" but when asked what kind of guy might tempt him he replied: "A smaller guy, not very hairy, maybe kind of girlish."
title: Auditions 21
